msgid "As a rule of thumb, each alpha will be based on `2.y.3.Final` of each minor version so will have the same feature set."
msgstr "作为一条经验法则，每个alpha版本将基于每个小版本的 `2.y.3.Final` ，因此将有相同的功能集。"

